attorneys: No attorney for appellant., George P. Blackburn, State’s Atty., of Austin, for the State.

opinions.opinion_text:
DAVIDSON, Commissioner.
Upon his plea of guilty before the court of the offense of burglary, appellant was convicted and assessed punishment at five years in the penitentiary.
The record before us contains neither a statement of facts nor bills of exception. Nothing is presented for review.
The judgment is affirmed.
Opinion approved by the Court.
